script to initialize hardhat project:-

yarn add --dev @openzeppelin/contracts @nomicfoundation/hardhat-toolbox @nomiclabs/hardhat-ethers@npm:hardhat-deploy-ethers ethers @nomiclabs/hardhat-etherscan @nomiclabs/hardhat-waffle chai ethereum-waffle hardhat hardhat-contract-sizer hardhat-deploy hardhat-gas-reporter prettier prettier-plugin-solidity solhint solidity-coverage dotenv @nomicfoundation/hardhat-network-helpers @nomicfoundation/hardhat-chai-matchers @typechain/hardhat typechain @typechain/ethers-v5 @ethersproject/abi @ethersproject/providers

yarn hardhat

scripts to check mistakes/inefficiencies in the code:-

yarn solhint contracts/*.sol

some important imports in hardhat.config.js file:-

require("@nomicfoundation/hardhat-toolbox");
require("@nomiclabs/hardhat-waffle")
require("@nomiclabs/hardhat-etherscan")
require("hardhat-deploy")
require("solidity-coverage")
require("hardhat-gas-reporter")
require("hardhat-contract-sizer")
require("dotenv").config()
